Bind the socket to the server port.
The port id should be obtained from the Homes file.
@c
		server.sin_family = AF_INET;
		server.sin_addr.s_addr = INADDR_ANY;
		server.sin_port = htons((unsigned short) ((p->port) & 0xFFFF));
